    "evidence_quotes": [
      "The final model was as follows: Ka (h-1)=θKa·Exp(ηKa); Vd (L/kg) =θVd·Exp(ηVd); CL (L·kg-1·h-1)=θCL·Exp(θNEWAEDs)Exp(θVPA)·Exp(θEIAEDs)·Exp(ηCL)",
