    "notes": "The model includes enzyme-inducing AEDs (carbamazepine, phenytoin, phenobarbital) and newer generation AEDs (levetiracetam, lamotrigine, topiramate). The model also accounts for the effect of valproic acid as an enzyme-inhibiting AED. The model was validated using both internal and external data."
